very much anymore.

01:12:27.350 --> 01:12:31.740
Usually, we think delta is
0.99, 0.95, or the like.

01:12:31.740 --> 01:12:34.210
So there's some
discounting in the future.

01:12:34.210 --> 01:12:37.390
You care more about stuff that's
one year from now compared

01:12:37.390 --> 01:12:39.800
to 10 years from now
or 30 years from now,

01:12:39.800 --> 01:12:41.350
but not that much differently.

01:12:41.350 --> 01:12:43.690
You care a lot about whether
