01:13:02.140 --> 01:13:04.420
is essentially you care
about the present 1,

01:13:04.420 --> 01:13:07.540
and then everything
in the future is 1/2.

01:13:07.540 --> 01:13:09.880
So again, relative
to the present,

01:13:09.880 --> 01:13:13.750
all future periods are
worth less, weighed 1/2.

01:13:13.750 --> 01:13:17.620
And then all discounting takes
place between the present

01:13:17.620 --> 01:13:20.740
and the immediate future.

01:13:20.740 --> 01:13:22.570
So then again, what
